Listing Agent Company: Franchise Realty, LLC

Listing Agent Company: The Real Estate Firm, Inc.
Description: Welcome to this immaculate 1890's George F. Barber Victorian home located 6 minutes from downtown Knoxville, nestled in the heart of Parkridge. You'll appreciate all of the incredible woodwork and preserved vintage details including: original staircase, large windows and 10' ceilings! This home features a beautifully renovated kitchen with Quartz counters, and a spacious pantry. On the main level you'll find a primary bedroom suite with spacious closet, renovated bath with custom tile and walk-in shower. Both bedrooms on 2nd floor has its own balcony!Complete renovation in compliance with Knox city construction code featuring new  electrical, plumbing, HVAC, roof, in wall insulation, double car concrete path, custom build kitchen cabinets, etc. Shower glass door in master bath is scheduled to be install.

Listing Agent Company: Highlands Elite Real Estate LLC
Description: Secluded living at its best! 4BR, 2BA on 1.5 acres w/ a 2car carport. Upgraded and updated!  All brick, one level home in a beautiful country setting w/ view of the mountains & below. Bonus room. Oversized laundry room. SS Appliances, propane gas oven, quartz countertops, custom butcher block on island in updated beautiful eat-in kitchen. Master suite with full bath & individual heat & cooling. New paint & flooring. 2 yr old roof. 30 x 50 shop with electricity & concrete floor. Very private with lots of wildlife. Barn on property as well.

Listing Agent Company: Keller Williams Realty
Description: Finally a fully renovated ranch in Lafollette for under 200K has hit the market. Not a stitch of carpet throughout the entire home so need to worry about allergies, spills, or messes. The kitchen is where the meals and memories are made so these quartz countertops, stainless appliances, and painted cabinets will transform your life. The recently updated HVAC allows for peace of mind for years to come. Staring at the North Cumberland Wildlife Management Area out your front door, you will feel like you have escaped into the country while being 1 mile from downtown. The dry crawl space has 15ft ceilings to use as storage or easily convert to a workshop.

Listing Agent Company: Byers & Harvey Inc.

Close to the mall and Downtown.

Listing Agent Company: Keller Williams Realty
Description: Stunning, move-in ready home completely remodeled from top to bottom! Located on a corner lot in quiet neighborhood just a couple of minutes to downtown Franklin! Open concept with beautiful modern design throughout. Newly refinished hardwood floors, new HVAC, new windows, all new light fixtures and recessed lighting, new kitchen with quartz counters, new Samsung appliances with wine fridge, new bathrooms with mosaic tile, large dedicated laundry room, new tankless water heater, new electric and plumbing, and so much more! The luxurious master ensuite has a large shower with modern tile and double vanities. Spacious bonus room could be used in so many ways. Newly repainted inside and out. Large carport and driveway and new professional landscaping.

Listing Agent Company: Offerpad Brokerage

Great home for entertaining with awesome back yard!

Listing Agent Company: Realty Executives Associates
Description: This charming 1940's storybook cottage has excellent appeal with a stone-cut marble exterior and sits on a corner lot. The home has a nice interior flow and looks like a Magnolia Style makeover!! Beautiful hardwood floors, built-in cupboards, and front entrance offer a yesteryear feel with a vestibule/foyer and a lovely front door. The living room is gorgeous and has beautiful hardwood floors, fireplace, arched doorway, and leads to a quaint side porch with arches and is quite cozy! The formal dining has lots of natural light and built-in cupboards. The breakfast room area is currently an office. The kitchen has quartz, tiled floors, SS Appliances, and a large farm sink. Two bedrooms and one bath on main. One bedroom and one bath upstairs.... The back patio is inviting, with steps that lead off to the detached garage. Located so conveniently to Bearden attractions and the Bearden Village Greenway runs through the Sutherland Ave side of the lot. This is a neighborhood that calls out, "Won't you be my neighbor." Call to schedule your exclusive showing. Showings begin Saturday, October 30th, 2021.

Listing Agent Company: Adams Realty, LLC

Listing Agent Company: Honors Real Estate Services LLC
Description:
RARE FIND, Beautiful Basement Ranch sitting on the 11th hole of the Links at Kahite Golf Course! RESORT LIVING in Tellico Village! The main level boasts gorgeous views and a spacious open floor plan. The family room features a see-thru fireplace and trey ceiling with under-mount lighting. Entertain  in your chef's kitchen with oversized island, custom cabinetry, quartz counters, double sink, stainless appliances and spacious eat-in kitchen nook.  Relax and take in the views from your screened deck or enjoy grilling on your separate grilling deck with room for a full size dining set. The main level primary suite offers a spa-like bathroom with jacuzzi, walk-in shower, separate double vanities, and large walk-in closet. Completing the main level is an office with double French doors and closet, and a dedicated laundry area with large sink and loads of cabinetry. Three inch hardwood floors cover most of the main level. 
The walk-out basement offers a kitchenette, wet bar, wine fridge, and cozy second family room and leads out to the patio overlooking the beautiful golf course. There are also 2 bedrooms and a full bath, second office or hobby room (could be golf cart storage) and 290 square feet of walk-in temp controlled storage. 
Additional features: New HVAC, new kitchenAid dishwasher and microwave, incredible view of the golf course, ceiling fans and deep trim throughout, oversized windows, glaze-stained mantle and trim surrounding fireplace, under cabinet lighting, upgraded safety screen on deck, lots of storage, oversized 2-car garage, 9' ceilings in basement. This immaculate home offers you the resort lifestyle you've been waiting for! Located in the resort community of Tellico Village. https://tellicovillage.org
Buyer to verify all information.
Update - Home is currently being painted with Benjamin Moore light gray.  Seller will have the white oak hardwood floors refinished, buyer to choose color with acceptable offer

Listing Agent Company: 901, REALTORS

Open floor plan and Brand New Kitchen with New SS Appliances with Print Shield, New Cabinetry & Island All with Soft Close Cabinets and Beautiful Quartz Counters. Listing Agent Company: Keller Williams Realty
Description: Newly renovated home in the desirable and convenient North Chattanooga community of Stuart Heights. The primary living areas provide open spaces that promote an atmosphere ideal for comfortable every day living, as well as entertaining. Upon entering the front doors, you are treated with a sweeping view of these open living areas - including the inviting foyer, the living and dining rooms, the gourmet kitchen and beyond to the the extra large deck where you will enjoy incredible mountain views. Renovations include a completely updated kitchen with new quartz countertops, all new appliances, including Miele dishwasher, Bosch refrigerator, Kitchen Aid convection oven and Kitchen Aid dual zone wine cooler. New Italian stainless kitchen and bar sinks incorporate touchless faucets with the bar sink providing filtered water. The lower level, 2 story apartment/office/in law-suite with separate entrance and parking has been completely updated to include new travertine marble floors, new carpet, modern vanity, plumbing fixtures and two of the three newly built decks. The living area is stubbed should you like to add a kitchenette and has one of the 3 gas fireplaces. The Master Bedroom Suite is like a retreat unto itself, and the current owner characterizes it as their "Shangri-La." It boasts 2 master baths with walk-in closets, various sitting areas, continuous crown molding, specialty ceiling, a wet bar, gas fireplace and a sunroom area that adds wonderful natural light and 2 additional closets. The additional bathrooms in the home have also been updated, and the seller can explain how to connect the wireless vanity speakers via Bluetooth to your cellphone. Plans were made as the area in the back of the property is perfect for an in ground pool and the new owner has the opportunity to complete the project. (Plans will be provided). Other new features include soaking tub, lovely new interior and exterior painting, and a 5 ton HVAC unit. Many more additional improvements are too extensive to list, as this amazing home has been completely and meticulously transformed to be move in ready. This exceptional almost 4,826 +/- square foot, 4 bedroom, 5 Â½ bath home sits on an almost .75 +/- acre lot and offers wonderful privacy on the decks and in the backyard. It is so peaceful that you will not believe you are only minutes from downtown Chattanooga. Take your time and relax on one of the home's four decks and realize that you can't hear traffic - only the sounds of the resident songbirds. Please call for more information and to schedule your private showing. Information is deemed reliable but not guaranteed. Buyer to verify any and all information they deem important.
